yy --> copy current line
yE --> copy next word

p --> paste

w (or W) --> move foward one word
b (or B) --> move backwards one word

i --> Start typing at the current place
a --> Start typing one characte ahead

$ --> end of line

A^{\mathrm{o}} --> Interior of A


Search and replace %s/wordtosearch/replacemente/action

%s/word/replacemente/g --> replaces all apparitions


:36,42s/Unix/Linux/g --> searchs an replace from line 36 to 42
